0.05 2026-05-05
 - reject bogus `0C` output from the macOS `osx-cpu-temp` backend
 - fall through to `powermetrics` or `iStats` when `osx-cpu-temp` returns an implausible zero reading
 - emit `°C` and `°F` unit labels in temperature output examples and payloads

0.04 2026-05-05
 - add a macOS Homebrew backend path for CPU temperature via `osx-cpu-temp`
 - try `osx-cpu-temp` before `powermetrics` or `iStats` on macOS

0.03 2026-05-05
 - suppress child stderr from quiet optional probes at the subprocess layer
 - keep macOS temperature fallback probing quiet when powermetrics or iStats are unavailable or require elevation

0.02 2026-05-05
 - fix macOS CPU temperature probing to retry supported powermetrics samplers
 - suppress missing optional sensor-backend noise from temperature probes
 - keep macOS fallback support for iStats on common Homebrew paths

0.01 2026-05-05
 - package the initial system-status DD skill
 - standardize disk, load, and temperature commands
 - add Linux, macOS, and Windows-aware code paths
 - add tests, docs, and release-gate records
